Package: duckbotos-browseros
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: wget, curl, gnupg2, apt-transport-https,
         xdg-utils,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: BrowserOS as the default browser for DuckBotOS
 Installs BrowserOS (https://github.com/browseros-ai/BrowserOS) as the
 default system web browser for DuckBotOS. BrowserOS is a Chromium-based
 browser with native AI agent support — Claude Code and Codex can run
 directly in-browser.
 .
 This package:
 - Adds the BrowserOS APT repository
 - Installs browseros-cli and the BrowserOS app
 - Sets BrowserOS as the default browser via update-alternatives and xdg-settings
 - Registers browseros-cli in PATH
 .
 The version installed matches the latest stable release from the
 BrowserOS GitHub releases page.
Homepage: https://github.com/browseros-ai/BrowserOS